data.description: Amazing location with lots of potential! This cozy cottage, situated in an established neighborhood in the Central area, is perfectly located for everyday convenience and outdoor adventure. A short drive will take you to historic sites like Sycamore Shoals State Park and the Elizabethton Covered Bridge; outdoor activities at Tannery Knobs Mountain Bike Park, Elizabethton Golf Course, and the Tweetsie Trail; and both ETSU and Milligan University. Happy Valley Elementary and High Schools are just 5 minutes away as well. The exterior of the home welcomes you to relax with a cup of coffee on the covered front porch or grill burgers on the spacious back deck overlooking the level back yard. The property includes a detached carport and three storage buildings, offering ample space for storage and protecting lawn equipment. Inside, the well-lit living room welcomes you with warmth and an inviting atmosphere, and the country kitchen and dining room provide the ideal setting for meals with family and friends. Don't miss the opportunity to put your personal touch on this delightful home! Schedule a showing today.
